00:07:40.820 --> 00:07:41.950
Liang Pin was the first

00:07:41.950 --> 00:07:43.370
to dare kill my woman.

00:07:43.950 --> 00:07:44.800
I hope

00:07:45.480 --> 00:07:47.200
