00:11:21.320 --> 00:11:23.250
Because I'm hypocritical enough.

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:24.240
That's actually

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:25.960
the most honest thing I've heard from you.

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:26.600
